column5: I finally mastered the Meegs presentation. Thank you misfish godfather. LOL  No ones more happier for you then I buddy. Well done
Once you get the knack, the rest is super easy!  S.
So I guess I can throw away the Williams. Lol.
<bowing down a la wayne and garth> "we're not worthy...we're not worthy..."
My name is Beans and I am an...oops...wrong posting... Nice whities Terry...WTG !

LOL, that's what I thought until my young buddy schooled me yesterday 15 - 2. Yes, I missed a few, but we can never take anything for granted. Had no problem last year hooking up. Just when I thought I had it mastered, life reminded me nothing is guaranteed. Couple of nice fish there Terry!

I usually do not open my flap of the hut to anyone. Propane is to expensive, heat is my best friend out there, but this morning ,he begged like I was the cod father. LOL A quick few pointers, the keys transfered to me for the yamadoo, is all it took. Next thing I heard was, about %^^^# time. Arms flying in the air and doing the newfie jig. Well it was close.
See, I made you infamous again.
